_sText:
A map I've been working on for a few weeks. I think its my best one so far. There are a total of 4 teleports in the map. You'll have to find them yourselves ;)

Thanks to Jaj for the skybox, and m3k for the batman model :D

Please assess and leave feedback!!!


This is only a Beta, so updated ones will come.

I think there is 44 spawns, don't trust me on it though! :P

There is also a breakable floor, on the long hallway up stairs. You'll have to find that also.
